headline: Does Airbnb’s Recent Share Slide Offer Long Term Value in 2025?
summary: Wondering if Airbnb is still a good buy after its big post pandemic run, or if the easy money has already been made? It may help to cut through the noise and zero in on what the current price is really offering you. Over the last week Airbnb has crept up about 1.5%, but it is still down roughly 6.5% over the past month and about 14.8% over the last year, even after a strong 29.5% gain over three years. That mix of short term weakness and longer term strength is exactly what makes the stock...

headline: 2 S&P 500 Stocks Worth Investigating and 1 We Brush Off
summary: The S&P 500 (^GSPC) is often seen as a benchmark for strong businesses, but that doesn’t mean every stock is worth owning. Some companies face significant challenges, whether it’s stagnating growth, heavy debt, or disruptive new competitors.
